728246f-a.title: Queens: Wyckoff Avenue - Summerfield Avenue
728246f-a.text:
Wyckoff Ave., north side, west from Summerfield Ave., showing the
Slocum House (third from corner; mansard roof; with dormer windows).
This house formerly stood on the south side of Wyckoff Ave. in ground
belonging to the Malt Diastase Company, located at the S.W. corner of
Wyckoff and Decatur Street.
January 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
